name: Fast Food Frenzy Fever
description:
Fast Food Frenzy Fever is an amazing adventure into a world of food. Watch food drops out of the sky.

Ensure to tap as fast as you can, to ensure not to miss any food. Click on special item to earn & double the points. The game is extremely addictive and will have you playing for hours on end.

Play Fast Food Frenzy Fever Today!
